Find the middle number.
=======================

n1 : get value
n2 : get value
n3 : get value

middle : choose from
	(n1) if between (n2) and (n3)
	(n2) if between (n1) and (n3)
	(n3) if between (n1) and (n2) ; or just "n3"

{ "The middle value is ", middle } ↲

=================================================

get value:
	ask for integer "Enter an integer: "

(n1) if between (n2) and (n3)::
	((n2 ≤ n1) and (n1 ≤ n3)) produces (n1)
	((n3 ≤ n1) and (n1 ≤ n2)) produces (n1)
